485
00:48:41,440 --> 00:48:43,870
That's why l so meticulously,

486
00:48:43,920 --> 00:48:46,190
almost in a documentary-like fashion,

487
00:48:46,240 --> 00:48:50,390
record the lengthy preparation

488
00:48:50,440 --> 00:48:54,310
to show what people are willing to do

489
00:48:54,360 --> 00:48:57,590
to satisfy their erotic fantasies -

490
00:48:57,640 --> 00:49:01,470
what they're prepared
to be subjected to.

